OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,FA man who sexually assaulted a 14-year-
OL,7,Fold girl as she was Harry Potter
OL,8,Fsightseeing in London has been fined
OL,9,F#400.
OL,11,FAbdul Barkeeh Salihi, 24, put his hand
OL,12,Fon the girl's bottom when she and her
OL,13,Ffamily were in Leadenhall Market, in
OL,14,Fthe City of London, to see the filming
OL,15,Flocation for Diagon Alley.
OL,17,FEarlier the same day, Salihi had
OL,18,Fslapped the bottom of a 42-year-old
OL,19,Fwoman after following her for a short
OL,20,Fdistance along nearby Lombard Street.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
