FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784720908
OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,FAfter the sexual assault on the girl,
OL,7,FSalihi was confronted by her family in
OL,8,Fthe Rocca restaurant in Leadenhall
OL,9,FMarket, in an incident which ended
OL,10,Fwith him throwing a chair through a
OL,11,Fwindow.
OL,13,FSalihi, an Afghan national, gave his
OL,14,Faddress to Inner London Crown Court as
OL,15,Fa hotel in Oxford which has been
OL,16,Fhousing asylum seekers.
OL,18,FHe admitted two counts of sexual
OL,19,Fassault and criminal damage, and was
OL,20,Fsentenced last week to a #400 fine
OL,21,Fwith a #160 victim surcharge.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
