OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784720908
OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,FSalihi will also be put on the sex
OL,7,Foffenders register for the next five
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,F"These were deeply distressing sexual
OL,11,Fassaults committed in broad daylight
OL,12,Fagainst two females who were simply
OL,13,Fgoing about their daily lives", said
OL,14,FDetective Constable Natalie Schofield,
OL,15,Ffrom City of London Police.
OL,17,F"One of the victims was just 14-years-
OL,18,Fold, making this offending
OL,19,Fparticularly concerning.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@^O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
