PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784720908
OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,F"I would like to thank both victims
OL,7,Ffor the immense courage they showed in
OL,8,Fcoming forward and supporting our
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"We know how difficult it can be to
OL,12,Freport sexual offences, and their
OL,13,Fbravery has ensured this offender has
OL,14,Fbeen held accountable for his actions."
OL,16,FLeadenhall Market dates back to the
OL,17,F14th century and was used in the
OL,18,Foriginal Harry Potter film franchise
OL,19,Fas a location for the Diagon Alley
OL,20,Fshopping street.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@gO]
