CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784720908
OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,FPolice said Salihi carried out the
OL,7,Ffirst sexual assault at around 3.30pm
OL,8,Fon January 28 last year when a woman
OL,9,Fwas walking along the road in the
OL,10,Frain, staying close to the buildings
OL,11,Ffor shelter.
OL,13,FSalihi emerged at Mansion House and
OL,14,Fbegan to follow the woman, coming up
OL,15,Fclose behind her until she turned and
OL,16,Fasked if he needed to get past.
OL,18,FPolice said Salihi shook his head,
OL,19,Fthen a few moments later slapped the
OL,20,Fwoman's bottom.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
