CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784720908
OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,FLater the same day, the girl who was
OL,7,Fsightseeing with her family felt a
OL,8,Ftouch on her bottom, and turned to see
OL,9,FSalihi with a "weird smirk on his
OL,10,Fface".
OL,12,FThe family went to the Rocca Italian
OL,13,Frestaurant and saw Salihi enter the
OL,14,Fsame premises, sparking a
OL,15,Fconfrontation where he was pushed
OL,16,Ftowards the counter and accused of
OL,17,Fsexual assault.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
