OL,3,CMan who groped teenage girl during
OL,4,CHarry Potter sightseeing tour fined
OL,6,FThe force said he initially refused to
OL,7,Fleave when asked by restaurant staff,
OL,8,Fand then "looked agitated" when he was
OL,9,Fsat outside.
OL,11,F"Salihi picked up a chair and threw it
OL,12,Fthrough a window", said the police.
OL,14,F"He picked up a second and threw it,
OL,15,Fbut this time it bounced against the
OL,16,Fglass."He was detained by members of
OL,17,Fthe public until police arrived."
